name: Dea Tore
content:
Dea Tore was a Human female doctor who stayed on Naboo during the Galactic Civil War.
Dea Tore appears in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online roleplaying game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. According to these files, Dr. Tore would have been on Naboo. However, Dr. Tore is not known to have appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character. Nevertheless, an emulated depiction pulled from this character's Interchange File Format reveals what she would have looked like if she were added to the game.
